It is absolutely outrageous that Donald Trump and Steve Mnuchin have still not approved grants included in the CARES Act to fully fund the paychecks and benefits of 2 million airline workers.

@stevenmnuchin1: Stop delaying these grants. Pay the airline workers now. https://twitter.com/FlyingWithSara/status/1248719302720720896 QT @FlyingWithSara We made history in the CARES Act by building a people’s bailout. Airlines applied for payroll grants w/ strict conditions: no layoffs, no stock buybacks, no dividends, cap exec comp. Any financial conditions on that $ will hurt workers, not airlines, not execs.
